  "content": "<script>!function(){if(document.querySelector('script[src*=\"cdn.tailwindcss\"]'))return;var t=document.createElement('script');t.src='https://cdn.tailwindcss.com';t.onload=function(){if(window.tailwind)tailwind.config={darkMode:'class',theme:{extend:{fontFamily:{sans:['Tajawal','sans-serif']}}}};};document.head.appendChild(t);}();</script>\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n<div class=\"font-[Tajawal] text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\" dir=\"rtl\">\n\n    <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed opacity-95 mb-6\">\n        <span class=\"font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400\">#تحديث</span> تطبيق المساعد الشخصي لتصميم منظومة الطاقة الشمسية. دليلك الشامل والهندسي الأول الذي يغنيك عن التخمين، صمم نظامك بالكامل بدقة علمية مطابقة لمعايير (NEC) العالمية.\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-950/30 border border-orange-200 dark:border-orange-900 rounded-2xl p-5 mb-8 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden\">\n        <div class=\"absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 rounded-full opacity-50\"></div>\n        <div class=\"relative z-10\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3 border-b border-orange-200 dark:border-orange-800 pb-3\">\n                <svg class=\"w-7 h-7 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\"></path></svg>\n                <h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-400 m-0\">تصميم وبرمجة حصرية</h3>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base\">\n                التطبيق من <strong>فكرتي وتصميمي الهندسي</strong>، وتمت برمجة النواة الحسابية الخاصة به كلياً وبشكل احترافي من خلال <span class=\"font-bold text-lg text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400\">الذكاء الاصطناعي (AI)</span> لضمان الخلو من الأخطاء ودقة المعادلات.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"flex justify-center my-8\">\n        <div class=\"w-24 h-24 sm:w-28 sm:h-28 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-800 bg-white flex items-center justify-center p-3\">\n            <svg class=\"w-full h-full text-orange-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M256 0a256 256 0 1 1 0 512A256 256 0 1 1 256 0zM135.2 267.4c-9.5-6.5-22.6-4.1-29.1 5.5s-4.1 22.6 5.5 29.1l80 54.9c7.2 4.9 16.6 4.9 23.8 0l160-109.7c9.5-6.5 11.9-19.6 5.4-29.1s-19.6-11.9-29.1-5.4L208 311 135.2 267.4z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"my-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-2xl mb-4 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 border-b-2 border-orange-100 dark:border-orange-900 pb-2 inline-block\">مرونة في الحساب وتقارير هندسية</h3>\n        <div class=\"text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed text-base mb-6\">\n            يوفر التطبيق طريقتين للحساب: إما <strong>التفصيلي حسب عدد الأجهزة</strong> أو الحساب المباشر <strong>حسب الأمبير وساعات التشغيل</strong>. مع ميزة تصدير كافة التفاصيل بضغطة زر إلى ملف PDF احترافي وجاهز.\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"bg-orange-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 border border-orange-100 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-3xl p-7 my-8 shadow-inner\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6\">\n            <span class=\"bg-orange-600 text-white w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl shadow-md text-xl flex-shrink-0\">\n                <svg class=\"w-7 h-7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>\n            </span>\n            <h3 class=\"font-bold text-2xl text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-300 m-0\">يسمح لك بتصميم المنظومة بالكامل:</h3>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"mb-5\">\n            <ul class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 list-none p-0 m-0\">\n                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-base\"><span class=\"text-orange-500 text-xl\">•</span> حساب الأحمال (واط/أمبير/طن)</li>\n                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-base\"><span class=\"text-orange-500 text-xl\">•</span> حجم بنك البطاريات والألواح</li>\n                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-base\"><span class=\"text-orange-500 text-xl\">•</span> توصيات الإنفرتر الذكية</li>\n                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-base\"><span class=\"text-orange-500 text-xl\">•</span> التكاليف التقريبية للمنظومة</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-orange-200 dark:border-slate-600\">\n            <strong class=\"text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-300 block mb-3 text-lg\">مميزات استثنائية وحالات مخصصة:</strong>\n            <ul class=\"space-y-2.5 list-none p-0 m-0\">\n                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-base\">\n                    <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path></svg>\n                    أمان مطابق لمعايير (NEC) العالمية للأسلاك والقواطع\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-base\">\n                    <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path></svg>\n                    دعم الحساب بدون بطاريات أو بدون ألواح (UPS)\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 text-base\">\n                    <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"></path></svg>\n                    الحساب حسب أوقات تواجد وإطفاء الكهرباء الوطنية\n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"my-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-5 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400\">روابط التحميل المباشرة للتطبيق</h3>\n\n        <div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.mediafire.com/file/nf3ddhfvrenno6j/solar_calculator_64-v8.apk/file\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n               class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-white text-gray-800 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-white py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl font-bold shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-full group\">\n                <svg class=\"w-7 h-7 shrink-0 text-orange-500 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path d=\"M318.7 268.7c-.2-36.7 15.6-64.1 39.6-79.6-18.6-26.1-45.8-30.5-55.7-31-25.4-2.6-48.1 15.1-61 15.1-13.2 0-32-14.9-52.5-14.5-26.8.5-51.4 15.6-65.2 39.6-27.9 48.3-7.2 119.3 19.9 158.3 13.3 19.1 29.2 40.6 50 39.8 20-.7 27.6-12.8 51.8-12.8 24.1 0 31 12.8 52.1 12.4 21.7-.3 34.9-19.5 48.2-39.1 15.2-22.1 21.5-43.5 21.8-44.5-.5-.2-42.3-16.2-42.6-63.2zM281.9 103.9c11.4-13.7 19-32.8 16.9-51.9-16.3.7-36.1 10.9-47.8 24.5-10.5 12.1-19.7 31.6-17.2 50.3 18.2 1.4 36.6-9.1 48.1-22.9z\"></path></svg>\n                <span class=\"text-base\">تنزيل للهواتف الحديثة (64-bit)</span>\n            </a>\n            <a href=\"https://www.mediafire.com/file/izd8m2orrhvkr77/solar_calculator_32-v7a.apk/file\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n               class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-white text-gray-800 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-white py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl font-bold shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-full group\">\n                <svg class=\"w-7 h-7 shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path d=\"M318.7 268.7c-.2-36.7 15.6-64.1 39.6-79.6-18.6-26.1-45.8-30.5-55.7-31-25.4-2.6-48.1 15.1-61 15.1-13.2 0-32-14.9-52.5-14.5-26.8.5-51.4 15.6-65.2 39.6-27.9 48.3-7.2 119.3 19.9 158.3 13.3 19.1 29.2 40.6 50 39.8 20-.7 27.6-12.8 51.8-12.8 24.1 0 31 12.8 52.1 12.4 21.7-.3 34.9-19.5 48.2-39.1 15.2-22.1 21.5-43.5 21.8-44.5-.5-.2-42.3-16.2-42.6-63.2zM281.9 103.9c11.4-13.7 19-32.8 16.9-51.9-16.3.7-36.1 10.9-47.8 24.5-10.5 12.1-19.7 31.6-17.2 50.3 18.2 1.4 36.6-9.1 48.1-22.9z\"></path></svg>\n                <span class=\"text-base\">تنزيل للهواتف القديمة (32-bit)</span>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-1 mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800\">\n        <a href=\"https://t.me/techtouch7/5548?single\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n           class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-4 bg-[#24A1DE] text-white py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hov